Name: Rawdon High Back Mesh Operator Chair With Fixed Arms - Black with Chrome Base
Short description:
• Butterfly style tilt mechanism
  • Added back support & stylish fixed arms
  • High density foam seat offering great comfort
  • High mesh back with faux leather head rest
  • Free next day delivery
Description:
The Rawdon high mesh back operator chair offers comfort and class at an affordable price, with added back support and fixed arms. The Rawdon enjoys an ultra-contemporary design to style any office or workstation. The faux leather headrest gives a more premium feel to a comfortable and affordable chair. The seat is made of a high density foam with great comfort and is upholstered in a high quality durable fabric.
The Rawdon chair features self extinguishing fireproof mesh and foam for increased workplace safety.

Chrome accents on the arms and base of the chair create a modern executive feel.

A 'butterfly' style tilt mechanism allows the user to lean back in their chair to change the angle of seating.

The Rawdon chair is lightweight and mobile, weighing in at just 12kg.

50mm easy-glide castors on a 320mm deluxe chrome 5-star base allow for easy, effortless movement across the workplace.
